    <div class="trust-item">Chamunda Nagar, Ajwa Rd, <strong>Vadodara</strong></div>
    <div class="trust-item"><strong>Open 24 Hours</strong></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 260 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M0 20 C 40 5, 60 5, 80 20 C 100 35, 120 35, 130 20 C 140 5, 160 5, 180 20 C 200 35, 220 35, 260 20" stroke="#c9a24b" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="130" cy="20" r="4" fill="#c9a24b"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div class="about-visual reveal">
      <div class="mono"></div>
      <div class="quote-mark">"Our venue was beautifully decorated by Eventeria... Anand bhai had a very professional approach to his work."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-copy reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Studio</div>
      <h2>Led personally by Anand Bhai and a team built on trust</h2>
      <p>Based on Ajwa Road in the heart of Vadodara, Eventeria has become the name Gujarati families call first — for the wedding sangeet, the first birthday, the baby shower, the mehendi evening. Not because of one grand event, but because of a hundred quietly perfect ones.</p>
      <p>The studio is known for arriving on time, decorating with care for the full length of the event, and sourcing everything a celebration needs — from florals and lighting to magicians and performers — so hosts can simply be present for their own occasion.</p>
      <div class="signature">— Anand Bhai, Founder</div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <div><div class="num">4.9 / 5</div><div class="lbl">Average Rating</div></div>
        <div><div class="num">102</div><div class="lbl">Verified Reviews</div></div>
        <div><div class="num">24 hrs</div><div class="lbl">Availability</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">What We Craft</div>
      <h2>Full-Service Event Design</h2>
      <p>Every celebration is planned, styled, and staged by the same team from first consultation to final teardown.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">01</span><h3>Wedding &amp; Sangeet Styling</h3><p>Mandap design, stage decor, lighting, and floral direction for every ceremony of the celebration.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">02</span><h3>Mehendi Design &amp; Setup</h3><p>Signature mehendi-evening styling — seating, backdrops, and ambience, paired with artist coordination.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">03</span><h3>Birthday Celebrations</h3><p>Themed decor for milestone birthdays, delivered exactly to brief and set up well ahead of arrival.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">04</span><h3>Baby Shower Décor</h3><p>Soft, colourful styling built around the family's theme, from balloon work to dessert tables.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">05</span><h3>Corporate &amp; Venue Styling</h3><p>Polished, on-brief decor for launches, offsites, and private venue functions across Vadodara.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card reveal"><span class="service-num">06</span><h3>Entertainment &amp; Talent Booking</h3><p>Magicians, performers, and entertainers sourced and coordinated as part of your event, end to end.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">How It Works</div>
      <h2>From First Call to Final Curtain</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-row">
      <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="stepno">01</div><h3>Consultation</h3><p>Call or message Eventeria with your date, venue, and vision — get a plan and price the same day.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="stepno">02</div><h3>Design &amp; Sourcing</h3><p>Decor, florals, lighting, and any entertainment are designed and booked around your theme and budget.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="stepno">03</div><h3>Setup &amp; Execution</h3><p>The team arrives early, styles the venue, and stays through the event to keep everything in place.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">In Their Words</div>
      <h2>102 Families, One Standard</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="test-grid">
